    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The night is hard and the night is long, but you know deep down, you can brave it.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Heroic Resolve, ability to gain martial focus, Cha 15 or Con 15, good alignment.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you activate heroic resolve and suppress a condition, you may instead suppress it for a number of rounds equal to the highest bonus between your Charisma or Constitution modifier.</p>\n<p>If the chosen condition originates from an evil-aligned creature or object or a creature or object with an evil aura or the evil sub-type, you may activate heroic resolve as a swift action.</p>\n",
